{"tid":1679464,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒，願意罷工罷課既入黎比正評","createTime":"2019-10-28T08:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T12:17:16.000Z","uid":104585,"like":72,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"90b4fc6f66a1a0db87f60a5e7eeb20a0cc37d2f3","tid":1679464,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:30:37.000Z","msg":"由10月4日開始，一直等緊罷工<br />\n個日幾多人嬲到震 即晚即刻出黎開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家出埋緊急法都唔罷工 等幾時啊<br />\n當時諗住學界/跨界別罷工組10月中收集完問卷之後會行動<br />\n但成個月都未有消息<br />\n唔想抗爭停滯不前 罷工在所難免<br />\n除左85罷工外 其他罷工失敗係因為唔夠宣傳倉促<br />\n如果認真搞 我信好多人會響應！<br />\n唔好再拖啦 愈拖香港人愈麻目<br />\n<br />\n會響應罷工既，留個正評比搞手 比信心佢地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"04631b216f837262280008f69d19968f8b9156bc","tid":1679464,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"fee408e8d7565f9f2b0993a75c99f86d6c323827","tid":1679464,"uid":21340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:32:10.000Z","msg":"想要多次8月5"},{"pid":"2d1015c6fe40a7cf0bd3bcdfedf9b7849edd5e3e","tid":1679464,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"G持<br />\n<br />\n大不了轉搵鬼佬Freelance"},{"pid":"4ca1d6283a2464a198ff10584e8391e6ca238f26","tid":1679464,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:34:57.000Z","msg":"一早罷緊"},{"pid":"4b19eedfb869b120c30448342df0d0260f43df18","tid":1679464,"uid":332036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"G持 罷工先係最有效而又唔會有手足比人拉"},{"pid":"8c995535d0c0613cc813eaf3768a419d13096221","tid":1679464,"uid":31545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:44:40.000Z","msg":"香港人最多罷一日，唔好期望香港人會長期罷工，<br />